'''鳥胸骨類'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|Ornithothoraces}}），又名'''鳥胸類'''，是一個包含所有[[反鳥類|反鳥亞綱]]和[[鸟|今鳥亞綱]]的[[鸟|鳥類]]分支。

鳥胸骨類的胸部高度進化，令它們具有特強的飛行能力。它們的[[喙突|喙突]]很長，[[胸骨|胸骨]]很大，改良了的肩膀關節盂，半剛硬的背部胸籃。最早已知的鳥胸骨類是1億4000萬年前[[中國|中國]]的[[原羽鳥|原羽鳥]]。<ref name="jinetal2008">{{Cite journal|title=On the horizon of Protopteryx and the early vertebrate fossil assemblages of the Jehol Biota|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s11434-008-0209-5|last=Jin|first=Fan|last2=Zhang|first2=FuCheng|date=2008-09|journal=Science Bulletin|issue=18|doi=10.1007/s11434-008-0209-5|volume=53|pages=2820–2827|language=en|issn=2095-9273|last3=Li|first3=ZhiHeng|last4=Zhang|first4=JiangYong|last5=Li|first5=Chun|last6=Zhou|first6=ZhongHe}}</ref>它們是[[伊比利亞鳥屬|伊比利亞鳥]]<ref name="Chiappe&Calvo1994">{{Cite journal|title=Neuquenornis volans , a new Late Cretaceous bird (Enantiornithes: Avisauridae) from Patagonia, Argentina|url=http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/02724634.1994.10011554|last=Chiappe|first=Luis M.|last2=Calvo|first2=Jorge O.|date=1994-06-22|journal=Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology|issue=2|doi=10.1080/02724634.1994.10011554|volume=14|pages=230–246|language=en|issn=0272-4634}}</ref><ref name="Chiappe1996">{{Cite journal|title=A Review of Dromaeosaurid Systematics and Paravian Phylogeny|url=http://www.bioone.org/doi/abs/10.1206/748.1|last=Turner|first=Alan H.|last2=Makovicky|first2=Peter J.|date=2012-08-17|journal=Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History|doi=10.1206/748.1|volume=371|pages=1–206|language=en|issn=0003-0090|last3=Norell|first3=Mark A.}}</ref>或[[中國鳥屬|中國鳥]]<ref name="Sereno1998">{{Cite journal|title=A rationale for phylogenetic definitions, with application to the higher-level taxonomy of Dinosauria [41-83 ]|url=http://www.schweizerbart.de/papers/njgpa/detail/210/88435/A_rationale_for_phylogenetic_definitions_with_appl?af=crossref|last=Sereno|first=Paul C.|date=1998-11-10|journal=Neues Jahrbuch für Geologie und Paläontologie - Abhandlungen|issue=1|doi=10.1127/njgpa/210/1998/41|volume=210|pages=41–83|language=en|issn=0077-7749}}</ref>及所有現存鳥類的共同祖先。

